    "default": {
      "title": "Molecular dynamics data for UDG enzyme",
      "description": "<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.57745/C5UQ2X\" target=\"_blank\">Lien vers les données</a><br>UDG enzyme-MD simulation. <br>  Initially, the UDG enzyme was solvated using the TIP3P water model, and 0.15 M sodium and chloride ions were added to neutralize the system. <br>  Before running the production MD, minimization and equilibration steps were performed on the UDG enzyme. The final MD production run was conducted on the system for 500 ns to obtain a stable configuration.  <br>  The 'input' folder contains the files necessary to run the simulation, while the 'output' folder contains the resulting trajectory.",
